Class Card

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.korupt.cards.Card
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CreditCard, DebitCard

    public abstract class Card
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    'Card' class will store common details of any type of cards. It implements 'Serializable' so that we can directly store its object in .dat/.txt file;
